title: Chancellor's big play allows Seattle to beat Detroit 13-10
text:
> Sports Chancellor's big play allows Seattle to beat Detroit 13-10 Seattle Seahawks strong safety Kam Chancellor, right, celebrates his tackle of Detroit Lions wide receiver Calvin Johnson in the second half of an NFL football game, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015, in Seattle. The Seahawks beat the Lions 13-10. (AP Photo/Scott Eklund)
